; evidence-grounding.form — grow tissue in its honest lane, or leave honest absence.
;
; THE ASK (Urs, 2026-06-09):
;   "is there a shape of a question we can ask to see if we find public observable evidence
;    to form new concepts around the missing code concepts?" — then: "can we embody this truth?"
;
;   It arrives from the shamballa light codes: some carried no concept-cell in our body, and
;   the question was whether we could honestly GROW one from public evidence rather than either
;   leaving the gap or fabricating a meaning. The shape generalizes far past the codes — it is
;   the gate for ANY claim that wants to enter the body.
;
; THE TRUTH — the body's lane-keeping discipline, run FORWARD to grow tissue:
;   1. STRIP to the testable kernel. Set the cosmology aside; ask: what publicly observable
;      phenomenon does the theme point at? ("the body at the speed of light" -> "does the body
;      measurably emit light?")
;   2. ASK across independent sources. What does replicable, public, independently-attested
;      evidence actually say about that kernel? No trusted prover — the three-way turned on the
;      world. The deep-research harness (fan-out search + adversarial verify + cited) is the carrier.
;   3. CLASSIFY the lane the answer lands in (the spectrum of evidence strength).
;   4. FORM the concept IN that lane — or leave honest absence. The lane is PART of the concept.
;
; THE LANES  (runnable: form-stdlib/evidence-grounding.fk · proven: tests/evidence-grounding-band.fk -> 127)
;   3 MEASURED   observed + independent + measured     -> evidence-lane concept, cited
;   2 PRACTICE   observed + independent, not measured  -> phenomenology concept, labeled as practice
;   1 INFERENCE  observed, but a single source         -> held as potential, not yet a concept
;   0 MYSTERY    no public observable kernel           -> honest absence / the symbol held unclaimed
;
;   eg-lane(claim) -> the lane ; eg-forms?(claim) -> grows tissue iff lane >= PRACTICE ;
;   eg-honest-absence?(claim) -> mystery, claim nothing ; eg-surface(claims) -> (grown held).
;
; SAME GATE AS value-execution.fk, turned toward concept-formation:
;   value-execution credits value only when EXECUTION is proven (ran + validated + served).
;   This credits a claim UP THE EVIDENCE SPECTRUM only as far as its evidence proves (observed
;   -> independent -> measured), and holds it in its honest lane below that — never fabricated
;   upward. A claim is "credited" to MEASURED only when measured; else held in PRACTICE,
;   INFERENCE, or MYSTERY, named, never inflated. Honest absence is honest.
;
; DEMONSTRATED ON THE CODES IT WAS BORN FROM (the band):
;   "999" body<->light -> MEASURED. The kernel is real: the human body emits ultraweak photon
;     emission (biophotons), imaged with cryogenic CCD, diurnal rhythm linked to metabolism;
;     a 56-study systematic review (PLOS One pone.0087401). BUT the lane discipline holds: the
;     MEASURED fact is "the body emits light"; the cosmology ("at the speed of light / ascension")
;     stays MYSTERY, named not asserted; UPE-as-diagnostic stays INFERENCE, contested. One code,
;     three lanes — the measurement never borrows the cosmology's robe.
;   "33" the sun -> MEASURED (heliotherapy / circadian / vitamin D).
;   "502" opalite egg -> PRACTICE (documented practice, no measured effect).
;   "777 888" dragons -> MYSTERY (no public kernel; honest absence, no fabrication).
;
; KINSHIP: satsang.fk (witness the outside, never pierce the inside) · shamballa-light-channel.fk
;   (bind only where the match is real) · value-execution.fk (proof over claim) · the CLAUDE.md
;   lane rule (keep evidence / inference / direct-experience / mystery / measured in their own
;   lanes). This is that rule made executable and generative.
;
; LINEAGE:
;   value-execution.fk (the gate) · the deep-research harness (step 2 carrier) · validate.sh
;   three-way (no trusted prover) · lc-codes-as-depth-not-dictionary (the surface vs the depth) ·
;   lc-observable-resonance-flow (external interactions as observable) · lc-trust-over-fear
;   (witness, not control) · lc-honest-lane (the human-facing teaching).
